license: OFL
category: handwriting
subsets: menu,latin

family: Amatic SC

designer: Vernon Adams

approved: true
description: <p>Amatic SC (Small Caps) \
  is a simple but effective hand drawn \
  webfont.</p> \
  <p>Amatic SC can be used for titling \
  and small runs of text. \
  It has been designed to be used \
  freely across the internet by web \
  browsers on desktop computers, \
  laptops and mobile devices.</p>
  
font.AmaticSC-Regular.ttf.style: normal
font.AmaticSC-Bold.ttf.style: normal

font.AmaticSC-Regular.ttf.weight: 400
font.AmaticSC-Bold.ttf.weight: 700 

